room_title: Escape room "Runaway Train" by Breakout Games - Cincinnati in Cincinnati
review: Went here for a family event and played the Runaway train. Lady named Val greeted us in the lobby and was very friendly. Our game master was the manager named Stephanie, she was awesome. We broke out with ten minutes to spare and only used two clues. Had a ton of fun. Highly recommend.

room_title: Escape room "Runaway Train" by Breakout Games - Cincinnati in Cincinnati
review: Great family fun! I highly recommend!

room_title: Escape room "Runaway Train" by Breakout Games - Cincinnati in Cincinnati
review: My dude Ryan helped us have a great experience with the Runaway Train. Definitely recommend doing it sometime with a big group of people. Definitely will come back.
